channel.title: I really need help with my 'run.exe'
channel.description:
oke, hello guys, this is kenvanbael i wanne make my own server but when i download a soucre and click run to test it there come; - starting... [launcher] Initing Cache... expection in thread "main" java.io.FileNotFoundExpection: data/cache/main_file_cache.dat2 <the system can not find the path specified> - at java.io.randomAccessFile.open<native method> - " " " " " " " ".<init><unknow source> - " " " " " " " ".<init><unknow source> - at com.alex.store.store.<init><store.java:25> - at com.alex.store.store.<init><store.java:19> - at com.rs.cache.Cache.init<cache.java:19> - at com.rs.Launcher.main<launcher.java:63> Press any key to continue
pleas help me how to fix this - if u help; tysm for your help!
greetz kenvanbael

item.title: I really need help with my 'run.exe'
item.dc:creator: @kenvanbael kenvanbael
item.description:
@kenvanbael wrote:

[quote=“RandQm, post:4, topic:447413”][quote author=kenvanbael link=topic=550310.msg4033448#msg4033448 date=1340985988]

FileNotFoundExpection: data/cache/main_file_cache.dat2 <het systeem kan het opgegeven - pad niet vinden>
lees de fout…
ergens in je files wordt dat pad ^ gezocht, maar is het niet aanwezig in je files.

read the error,
somewhere in your files something searches that pad, but it isn’t able to find it.

en hoe kom ik aan dat file? dat is het probleem dat weet ik niet
& how i come on that file, thats the problem i don’t know how to get it
[/quote]

kijk eerst of je het hebt, misschien is het fout getiteld als anti-leech.
anders kijk je welke cache versie gebruikt word en rip je die file uit een andere server.

First look if you don’t have the file, maybe is titled wrong as anti-leech,
else look which cache version you have and rip it out of another server.[/quote]

wel ik heb juist gekeken en ik heb het niet :o

well i just looked and i don’t got that file ;o
